==German==
===Etymology===
Related to Indo-European ''*leu-'' "to [[detach]]". Compare Greek ''lyo'' "I liberate", Latin ''[[solvere]]'' "to [[dissolve]]", English ''[[forlorn]]''.
===Verb===
'''verlieren'''
# to [[lose]] (something, or a game)
# (''sich verlieren''): to [[trail]] [[away]]

